author: @Yvagne
content: The joy and love showed by the spectators and fans were all heartfelt just by watching the videos. That's one first class Madonna concert. I wish I could visit Brazil someday to feel your energy. Enviando amor das Filipinas. 🇵🇭❤🇧🇷
